  <name>shepard plugin — fileformat CAD (STEP/3DXML/JT/OBJ metadata parser)</name>
  <description>
    Metadata parser for CAD exchange formats common in aerospace composite
    manufacturing (MFFD / DLR ZLP Augsburg context). Supports STEP ISO 10303-21
    header + partial AP242 DATA section, Dassault 3DXML ZIP+XML product metadata,
    JT magic-byte detection, and OBJ mesh statistics. Emits urn:shepard:cad:* and
    urn:shepard:mffd:cad:* SemanticAnnotations on file upload. No geometry
    rendering in phase 1 (deferred to CAD-RENDER-1 + glTF ViewRecipeRenderer).
  </description>
